com.dd.plist

Class NSSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dd.plist.NSObject
      • com.dd.plist.NSSet

  • public class NSSet
extends NSObject
    The NSSet class is an unordered collection of NSObject instances. This implementation uses a LinkedHashSet or TreeSetas the underlying data structure.
    Author:
    Daniel Dreibrodt
    See Also:
    LinkedHashSet
